query: select DESPATCH_DATE as 'Despatch Date', CUSTOMER_NUMBER, PART_CODE, WAREHOUSE from DESPATCH_NOTES where COMPANY_CODE = '{{company_code}}' and DIVISION = '{{warehouse}}' and DESPATCH_NOTE = '{{part_job}}' and DESPATCH_LINE  = '{{line_lot_stage}}'
select TOP(10) FORMAT (DESPATCH_DATE, 'dd-MM-yy') as 'Dispatch Date', CUSTOMER_NUMBER as 'Cust No' from DESPATCH_NOTES
select EMP_ID "Emp ID", FIRST_NAME "First Name", LAST_NAME "Last Name", USER_NAME "User name" from emp
